{
  "texts": [
    "There may be a further version control risk involved if the foundational model used to develop the internal LLM from is updated.",
    "Further guidance and regulation on the use of LLMs may help guide potential risk-controlled adoption.",
    "As some of the aforementioned use cases show, LLMs have various indirect applications where actuarial work is concerned (e.g.",
    "assistance with coding).",
    "Indirect applications refer to the use of LLMs to assist a practitioner with their work, whereas direct applications refer to LLMs that serve a distinct role in a process (Balona, 2023)."
  ]
}